    "biography": "<p>An insect spirit worker in its true form — the colony's labour caste, tending cocoons and larvae. Dual-natured but a poor combatant. Attributes scale with Force (here F = 3): Body F−2, Quickness F×3, Strength F+2, Charisma/Willpower F, Intelligence F−2, Essence F(A), Reaction F; no armour.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Enhanced Senses (Smell), Skill. <strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Reduced Senses (Sight), Vulnerability (Insecticides).</p><p><em>True Reaction = Force (3). Initiative +10 manifest (included: 13 + 1D6), +20 astral. GM Information, Double Exposure p.48.</em></p>",
